      <wp_comment_content><![CDATA[Wow! Just wow! Anarchists fighting ISIL (or ISIS or IS or whatever stupid name they're calling themselves at the moment, my partner calls them EyeSore. An eyesore according to Wikipedia is something considered to look unpleasant or ugly, examples include dilapidated buildings, litter and polluted areas. Natural eyesores include mud, weeds and feces, an apt description for IS). I had no idea Turkish anarchists were supporting Kurdish fighters in Kobanê, in fact I had no idea that anarchism existed anywhere in the Middle East at all. I so hope that one day there will be an independent Kurdistan, that will include Kurds, Arabs, Yazidi and all minorities who pine for freedom and nothing more, it's not a big ask is it? The guys and girls of DAF are my new heroes, and I want one of their t-shirts with headscarf included. Be brave DAF and remember freedom is all that matters to an anarchist, it is our job to protect the democratic rights of all peoples to be free, because without freedom we are the living dead.]]></wp_comment_content>
